[
  {
    "id": "1CH.8.1",
    "book": "1 Chronicles",
    "bookNum": 13,
    "bookAbbrev": "1CH",
    "chapter": 8,
    "verse": 1,
    "text": "Now Benjamin begat Bela his firstborn, Ashbel the second, and Aharah the third,",
    "hash": "948f2b65d2e667dfdd93b9b065c10069dc85870861d8f38db9da52bcd11e0260"
  },
  {
    "id": "1CH.8.2",
    "book": "1 Chronicles",
    "bookNum": 13,
    "bookAbbrev": "1CH",
    "chapter": 8,
    "verse": 2,
    "text": "Nohah the fourth, and Rapha the fifth.",
    "hash": "7fef4625397e62ab91886c9a0c9a33ae50c0f624faa45fc83077691c73ce1bac"
  },
  {
    "id": "1CH.8.3",
    "book": "1 Chronicles",
    "bookNum": 13,
    "bookAbbrev": "1CH",
    "chapter": 8,
    "verse": 3,
    "text": "And the sons of Bela were, Addar, and Gera, and Abihud, {Addar: or, Ard}",
    "hash": "e9a20f84a6df9ff36f55fe471bd25cb7fcf5408191bed39981bab6e8f44eaaf6"
  },
  {
    "id": "1CH.8.4",
    "book": "1 Chronicles",
    "bookNum": 13,
    "bookAbbrev": "1CH",
    "chapter": 8,
    "verse": 4,
    "text": "And Abishua, and Naaman, and Ahoah,",
    "hash": "b80457060dae7a2c6e0f24376a9d0c1e7e10085386cd7918210e9c223b7c6f1f"
  },
  {
    "id": "1CH.8.5",
    "book": "1 Chronicles",
    "bookNum": 13,
    "bookAbbrev": "1CH",
    "chapter": 8,
    "verse": 5,
    "text": "And Gera, and Shephuphan, and Huram. {Shephuphan: or, Shupham}",
    "hash": "00bad9df566b4ae4ad45a8299b5ac543bda20672c7e34f6c097206be5f6cad52"
  },
  {
    "id": "1CH.8.6",
    "book": "1 Chronicles",
    "bookNum": 13,
    "bookAbbrev": "1CH",
    "chapter": 8,
    "verse": 6,
    "text": "And these {are} the sons of Ehud: these are the heads of the fathers of the inhabitants of Geba, and they removed them to Manahath:",
    "hash": "87a34043d0197d328c77f25cbe03f285fd8b800a207fe28206f82ec283cda6b2"
  },
  {
    "id": "1CH.8.7",
    "book": "1 Chronicles",
    "bookNum": 13,
    "bookAbbrev": "1CH",
    "chapter": 8,
    "verse": 7,
    "text": "And Naaman, and Ahiah, and Gera, he removed them, and begat Uzza, and Ahihud.",
    "hash": "a5d4dfd027966fa9f98c0fd44fc441c9b959d5587a5ad63fca157943613c018e"
  },
  {
    "id": "1CH.8.8",
    "book": "1 Chronicles",
    "bookNum": 13,
    "bookAbbrev": "1CH",
    "chapter": 8,
    "verse": 8,
    "text": "And Shaharaim begat {children} in the country of Moab, after he had sent them away; Hushim and Baara {were} his wives.",
    "hash": "a408ad380c86327e048fa78fcd937cab427b4c20bd60e3cef2c2f3125b3725ab"
  },
  {
    "id": "1CH.8.9",
    "book": "1 Chronicles",
    "bookNum": 13,
    "bookAbbrev": "1CH",
    "chapter": 8,
    "verse": 9,
    "text": "And he begat of Hodesh his wife, Jobab, and Zibia, and Mesha, and Malcham,",
    "hash": "9af625b1e34f4954ee3c21550db8363761ea53cf000718962fddfe6cf060e38a"
  },
  {
    "id": "1CH.8.10",
    "book": "1 Chronicles",
    "bookNum": 13,
    "bookAbbrev": "1CH",
    "chapter": 8,
    "verse": 10,
    "text": "And Jeuz, and Shachia, and Mirma. These {were} his sons, heads of the fathers.",
    "hash": "ecf17803a3eedefde1878020de12f0b215aeaaaadecfd8db59a9fb6c89b4807a"
  },
  {
    "id": "1CH.8.11",
    "book": "1 Chronicles",
    "bookNum": 13,
    "bookAbbrev": "1CH",
    "chapter": 8,
    "verse": 11,
    "text": "And of Hushim he begat Abitub, and Elpaal.",
    "hash": "18a5cbadd06554119bfb05d3fea0956147e2aa5c465dae98e296af4f11a25c49"
  },
  {
    "id": "1CH.8.12",
    "book": "1 Chronicles",
    "bookNum": 13,
    "bookAbbrev": "1CH",
    "chapter": 8,
    "verse": 12,
    "text": "The sons of Elpaal; Eber, and Misham, and Shamed, who built Ono, and Lod, with the towns thereof:",
    "hash": "1a0db69c8364a6d253b506a9412eacccc5aa1c962e5a12bffe9ea27387542e8a"
  },
  {
    "id": "1CH.8.13",
    "book": "1 Chronicles",
    "bookNum": 13,
    "bookAbbrev": "1CH",
    "chapter": 8,
    "verse": 13,
    "text": "Beriah also, and Shema, who {were} heads of the fathers of the inhabitants of Aijalon, who drove away the inhabitants of Gath:",
    "hash": "beeae7a70bae452a774a2483d8fec4fe552ef5b5f9ec75a465c39cf63fe2c85c"
  },
  {
    "id": "1CH.8.14",
    "book": "1 Chronicles",
    "bookNum": 13,
    "bookAbbrev": "1CH",
    "chapter": 8,
    "verse": 14,
    "text": "And Ahio, Shashak, and Jeremoth,",
    "hash": "505450d455c2fa30b94be16f1f299f0d587b2c9d558d30ec9348b9edaf4e8eb9"
  },
  {
    "id": "1CH.8.15",
    "book": "1 Chronicles",
    "bookNum": 13,
    "bookAbbrev": "1CH",
    "chapter": 8,
    "verse": 15,
    "text": "And Zebadiah, and Arad, and Ader,",
    "hash": "e17ac280d780120a1093f38dbf284b4d5ca5c82009e428df2aedcb7fdcb71f40"
  },
  {
    "id": "1CH.8.16",
    "book": "1 Chronicles",
    "bookNum": 13,
    "bookAbbrev": "1CH",
    "chapter": 8,
    "verse": 16,
    "text": "And Michael, and Ispah, and Joha, the sons of Beriah;",
    "hash": "4856d1fff0e7d1a9d046a9448bf54c91e361e8451e6609cdef1001a03706df32"
  },
  {
    "id": "1CH.8.17",
    "book": "1 Chronicles",
    "bookNum": 13,
    "bookAbbrev": "1CH",
    "chapter": 8,
    "verse": 17,
    "text": "And Zebadiah, and Meshullam, and Hezeki, and Heber,",
    "hash": "857077672becedbbc2ce55e133d91a3c6c221ddd766b8102b82a968b32cd02c6"
  },
  {
    "id": "1CH.8.18",
    "book": "1 Chronicles",
    "bookNum": 13,
    "bookAbbrev": "1CH",
    "chapter": 8,
    "verse": 18,
    "text": "Ishmerai also, and Jezliah, and Jobab, the sons of Elpaal;",
    "hash": "ff723844b90de73f7486278113ba33c017386fdbb482268af3b1c624f75e2b3c"
  },
  {
    "id": "1CH.8.19",
    "book": "1 Chronicles",
    "bookNum": 13,
    "bookAbbrev": "1CH",
    "chapter": 8,
    "verse": 19,
    "text": "And Jakim, and Zichri, and Zabdi,",
    "hash": "bc7353cac4737acbe1736d6b9b67adeddd6c09a49ef131689fbc3c6fcf548df9"
  },
  {
    "id": "1CH.8.20",
    "book": "1 Chronicles",
    "bookNum": 13,
    "bookAbbrev": "1CH",
    "chapter": 8,
    "verse": 20,
    "text": "And Elienai, and Zilthai, and Eliel,",
    "hash": "c15888be06cd99d3e5993fb084dc6aab65a3359bca167a82fb9b6e0c51eadab6"
  },
  {
    "id": "1CH.8.21",
    "book": "1 Chronicles",
    "bookNum": 13,
    "bookAbbrev": "1CH",
    "chapter": 8,
    "verse": 21,
    "text": "And Adaiah, and Beraiah, and Shimrath, the sons of Shimhi; {Shimhi: or, Shema}",
    "hash": "ebbcd82135e76c1fb643d3797715305cc7236fd27bcba230420ac17b479884e6"
  },
  {
    "id": "1CH.8.22",
    "book": "1 Chronicles",
    "bookNum": 13,
    "bookAbbrev": "1CH",
    "chapter": 8,
    "verse": 22,
    "text": "And Ishpan, and Heber, and Eliel,",
    "hash": "9ee202d1e6234c7d537f46cf2152c824c4658ccbc2d0464da0d8b5bd7d1589bd"
  },
  {
    "id": "1CH.8.23",
    "book": "1 Chronicles",
    "bookNum": 13,
    "bookAbbrev": "1CH",
    "chapter": 8,
    "verse": 23,
    "text": "And Abdon, and Zichri, and Hanan,",
    "hash": "952118c208e5c87be531d4616d6ed122873f664f2e9df7e52148da22dfc1af1a"
  },
  {
    "id": "1CH.8.24",
    "book": "1 Chronicles",
    "bookNum": 13,
    "bookAbbrev": "1CH",
    "chapter": 8,
    "verse": 24,
    "text": "And Hananiah, and Elam, and Antothijah,",
    "hash": "dada518f89e162ae55dee04a75a291dbd15b4669b8517e37f44fb59f1cebcb91"
  },
  {
    "id": "1CH.8.25",
    "book": "1 Chronicles",
    "bookNum": 13,
    "bookAbbrev": "1CH",
    "chapter": 8,
    "verse": 25,
    "text": "And Iphedeiah, and Penuel, the sons of Shashak;",
    "hash": "92e03b6936779c607bd07d863e3491a7e43526484c6b6ae16a476fbb48b58706"
  },
  {
    "id": "1CH.8.26",
    "book": "1 Chronicles",
    "bookNum": 13,
    "bookAbbrev": "1CH",
    "chapter": 8,
    "verse": 26,
    "text": "And Shamsherai, and Shehariah, and Athaliah,",
    "hash": "b57a44c47d420552e69c6710ba35b989933548d73366cecda837c5bba1becbaa"
  },
  {
    "id": "1CH.8.27",
    "book": "1 Chronicles",
    "bookNum": 13,
    "bookAbbrev": "1CH",
    "chapter": 8,
    "verse": 27,
    "text": "And Jaresiah, and Eliah, and Zichri, the sons of Jeroham.",
    "hash": "b07019d8da2e052323319e2bd087eb996b8394211a6011eb6868acce72318270"
  },
  {
    "id": "1CH.8.28",
    "book": "1 Chronicles",
    "bookNum": 13,
    "bookAbbrev": "1CH",
    "chapter": 8,
    "verse": 28,
    "text": "These {were} heads of the fathers, by their generations, chief {men}. These dwelt in Jerusalem.",
    "hash": "ca6c129546f4749b94ec46d22514bccf9805d6e1e45b35f8324a5aedbc6b3249"
  },
  {
    "id": "1CH.8.29",
    "book": "1 Chronicles",
    "bookNum": 13,
    "bookAbbrev": "1CH",
    "chapter": 8,
    "verse": 29,
    "text": "And at Gibeon dwelt the father of Gibeon; whose wife's name {was} Maachah: {father...: also called Jehiel}",
    "hash": "7d05adbf9fd7e59fb47e7fb83ce27a27fd25652e1ba64a081078a8acc1cfcc65"
  },
  {
    "id": "1CH.8.30",
    "book": "1 Chronicles",
    "bookNum": 13,
    "bookAbbrev": "1CH",
    "chapter": 8,
    "verse": 30,
    "text": "And his firstborn son Abdon, and Zur, and Kish, and Baal, and Nadab,",
    "hash": "be24d40015599155b7690f72de5d071b797f216d6518d3aac40948859a963396"
  },
  {
    "id": "1CH.8.31",
    "book": "1 Chronicles",
    "bookNum": 13,
    "bookAbbrev": "1CH",
    "chapter": 8,
    "verse": 31,
    "text": "And Gedor, and Ahio, and Zacher. {Zacher: or, Zechariah}",
    "hash": "c4edb563cea17d4a97b7c007891eea165f397fb9d83737acc075fba4dc3c2b13"
  },
  {
    "id": "1CH.8.32",
    "book": "1 Chronicles",
    "bookNum": 13,
    "bookAbbrev": "1CH",
    "chapter": 8,
    "verse": 32,
    "text": "And Mikloth begat Shimeah. And these also dwelt with their brethren in Jerusalem, over against them. {Shimeah: or, Shimeam}",
    "hash": "6586b41f6c45e1e940bb39df0fa3854370c34ffa75144707de5f1163810d96fc"
  },
  {
    "id": "1CH.8.33",
    "book": "1 Chronicles",
    "bookNum": 13,
    "bookAbbrev": "1CH",
    "chapter": 8,
    "verse": 33,
    "text": "And Ner begat Kish, and Kish begat Saul, and Saul begat Jonathan, and Malchishua, and Abinadab, and Eshbaal. {Abinadab: also called, Ishui} {Eshbaal: or, Ishbosheth}",
    "hash": "d0276ea5e0e852b3b54b1090a0df97b05871e9a72e581d57b5d89465c2127454"
  },
  {
    "id": "1CH.8.34",
    "book": "1 Chronicles",
    "bookNum": 13,
    "bookAbbrev": "1CH",
    "chapter": 8,
    "verse": 34,
    "text": "And the son of Jonathan {was} Meribbaal; and Meribbaal begat Micah. {Meribbaal: or, Mephibosheth}",
    "hash": "0a503f01059c02f009b9dc8bd10de4490706d3c91c8e4ea2956716a968a20898"
  },
  {
    "id": "1CH.8.35",
    "book": "1 Chronicles",
    "bookNum": 13,
    "bookAbbrev": "1CH",
    "chapter": 8,
    "verse": 35,
    "text": "And the sons of Micah {were}, Pithon, and Melech, and Tarea, and Ahaz. {Tarea: or, Tahrea}",
    "hash": "c974015b980c31603e6b62f0eac1aa1a33544468f85d2aa6027fb52d2fbcb383"
  },
  {
    "id": "1CH.8.36",
    "book": "1 Chronicles",
    "bookNum": 13,
    "bookAbbrev": "1CH",
    "chapter": 8,
    "verse": 36,
    "text": "And Ahaz begat Jehoadah; and Jehoadah begat Alemeth, and Azmaveth, and Zimri; and Zimri begat Moza, {Jehoadah: also called, Jarah}",
    "hash": "59f711e314b2e3ed47223fdd532013639e1d91538daecd335741514693421a3a"
  },
  {
    "id": "1CH.8.37",
    "book": "1 Chronicles",
    "bookNum": 13,
    "bookAbbrev": "1CH",
    "chapter": 8,
    "verse": 37,
    "text": "And Moza begat Binea: Rapha {was} his son, Eleasah his son, Azel his son: {Rapha: also called, Rephaiah}",
    "hash": "810813a1633e3cf16042a44534b458a0461a3beb11aa27909ba4b8beb5115be5"
  },
  {
    "id": "1CH.8.38",
    "book": "1 Chronicles",
    "bookNum": 13,
    "bookAbbrev": "1CH",
    "chapter": 8,
    "verse": 38,
    "text": "And Azel had six sons, whose names {are} these, Azrikam, Bocheru, and Ishmael, and Sheariah, and Obadiah, and Hanan. All these {were} the sons of Azel.",
    "hash": "5929c5237a65cc88db763ce35105cd493aa9f5b7f0ee942a52ac15b13d05b066"
  },
  {
    "id": "1CH.8.39",
    "book": "1 Chronicles",
    "bookNum": 13,
    "bookAbbrev": "1CH",
    "chapter": 8,
    "verse": 39,
    "text": "And the sons of Eshek his brother {were}, Ulam his firstborn, Jehush the second, and Eliphelet the third.",
    "hash": "7ab9bb1e08c8ff6faa00485a35fb4df4efe68bfa5017c2dc4835da4d036bea4a"
  },
  {
    "id": "1CH.8.40",
    "book": "1 Chronicles",
    "bookNum": 13,
    "bookAbbrev": "1CH",
    "chapter": 8,
    "verse": 40,
    "text": "And the sons of Ulam were mighty men of valour, archers, and had many sons, and sons' sons, an hundred and fifty. All these {are} of the sons of Benjamin.",
    "hash": "042d5ca75ca5f115de932ccf6526c11961b30500b8b4bf88b06d857d0ea11f5f"
  }
]